headline: Nordson Test & Inspection Receives Top Honor with Prime Step-by-Step Innovation Award for SQ3000M2 System
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, November 13, 2024--Nordson Test & Inspection today announced that it has earned the Prime Award, which is the top honor, at the Step-by-Step Excellence Awards (SbSEA) for its groundbreaking SQ3000M2 Automated Optical Inspection (AOI) and Metrology System. The award was presented during a recent ceremony at NEPCON Asia.
